	(text "8: 8x GPI dipswitch    \n4: 2x UART naar TC2070\n4: 4x Status LEDs (GPO) green, orange, red, blue\n* 4: SPI naar TMC5160\n* 4: JTAG interface\n2: I2C Temp sensor\n* 2: CAN Interface\n4: ADC psu measurement (3V3, 5V, 12V, 48V)\n3: ADC Rev. measurement (boardtype, hwrev, assy)\n1: ADC ACS725 current sensor\n1: 48V Softstart control line GPO\n3: Encoder A, B, Z (GPI inputs, quadrature encoder input/ timer? )\n1: Endstop switch (GPI)\n-----+\n45\n\n\n"
